06:20.927 --> 06:26.198
Unless, of course, the client
is the catholic church?

06:26.199 --> 06:28.734
- We'll know for sure once
we subpoena your records.

06:28.735 --> 06:31.570
This isn't Switzerland.

06:31.571 --> 06:33.672
- Theresa was senior v.P.

06:33.673 --> 06:35.507
In charge of the victims
settlement account

06:35.508 --> 06:37.876
