archdiocese of New York.

06:37.877 --> 06:40.612
- Victims of abuse by priests.

06:40.613 --> 06:43.949
- Yes.

06:43.950 --> 06:48.820
- Now, aren't there any
better jobs in this bank

06:48.821 --> 06:56.962
for a woman of, you
know, her skills?

06:56.963 --> 07:00.065
- Theresa felt very strongly
about remunerating victims.

07:00.066 --> 07:01.600
