07:01.601 --> 07:03.568
and restore the good
name of the church.

07:03.569 --> 07:07.172
- So the wire transfer was a
settlement to bn individual?

07:07.173 --> 07:09.040
- Yes.

07:09.041 --> 07:12.010
- She have any help
with that account?

07:12.011 --> 07:13.445
- I helped Theresa

07:13.446 --> 07:15.180
